        <div class="fix-step-desc">Your <code style="font-family:'Courier Prime',monospace;color:var(--blue)">static.yml</code> must include the correct permissions block. Without <code style="font-family:'Courier Prime',monospace;color:var(--blue)">pages: write</code> and <code style="font-family:'Courier Prime',monospace;color:var(--blue)">id-token: write</code>, the deploy step will always fail.</div>
        <div class="code-inline">permissions:<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;pages: write<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;id-token: write<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;contents: read</div>
      </div>
      <div class="fix-step">
        <div class="fix-step-num">03</div>
